<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="typification">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Typification.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">There appears to be no syntype at Madrid so we have selected the specimen at OXF as the lectotype as this is a more complete specimen than that at Paris.</paragraph>
